FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779379877
OL,3,CSupporters see fresh chance to revive
OL,4,Cthe assisted dying bill
OL,6,FThe most supportive of them is thought
OL,7,Fto be the Liberal Democrat MP Andrew
OL,8,FGeorge, who was drawn in fourth place.
OL,10,FHe has been highly critical of the
OL,11,Ffact that the bill ran out of time in
OL,12,Fthe House of Lords before any vote
OL,13,Fcould take place, in what supporters
OL,14,Fclaim was a deliberate attempt to
OL,15,Ffilibuster it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
