CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779379877
OL,3,CSupporters see fresh chance to revive
OL,4,Cthe assisted dying bill
OL,6,FIt is not known whether her enthusiasm
OL,7,Fis great enough to consider bringing
OL,8,Fthe same bill again, however.
OL,10,FOpponents argue that scrutiny in the
OL,11,FHouse of Lords highlighted serious
OL,12,Fflaws in the bill and strongly object
OL,13,Fto the accusation of filibustering.
OL,15,FIn an interview shortly before the
OL,16,Fballot was drawn, former Health
OL,17,FMinister Ashley Dalton, who has
OL,18,Fmetastatic breast cancer, warned her
OL,19,Fcolleagues against reviving it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
